&lt;p&gt;Opportunities have arisen for enthusiastic and highly skilled Band 6 Physiotherapists to join our musculoskeletal outpatient’s team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;There are permanent full time and part time posts available.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The post holders will rotate around locations within the Calderdale and Huddersfield health economy, working in lively and friendly teams where you will have support on an informal basis and through formal supervision and annual appraisal.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In addition to mandatory training you will have opportunities to participate in relevant in-service training as part of continual professional development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Full Time and part time permanent hours available.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
